column5: Insert Bare Naked Ladies Tune "If I had a million dollars..."  here...  http://www.alaskayachtcharters.com/index.php  What an adventure that would be....
Those prices are unreal!!! imagine how nice of a boat you can buy for that much lol

That would be an awsome trip to go on.  Although I would prefer the money go towards a boat.  Just gotta find 5 people to go in on it with me.  Still cheaper than a week of Heli-boarding at Weigle's in B.C.
dang, big cash and licence booze isn't even included
When you think about it at $4000 a person it's compares quite favourably to other Alaska resorts out there. Most that I have looked at are in the $3500-$5000 range for 5 days, all in of course.
I think that if you had alot of dough.. i mean alot of dough.. you could spend some time doing stuff like that.
If ya can dream it..you can do it!
